ins, and some are entered directly by a user in the form of status update. To help manage the different activity types, use the filter dropdown box to switch between them.'=>'有許多不同類型的活動。有些是由 BuddyPress 和其他外掛自動生成，有些是由使用者以狀態更新的形式直接輸入而成。
若要協助管理不同類型的活動，請使用「篩選器」的下拉式選單間進行切換。','Activity items per page (screen options)Activity'=>'活動','You can manage activities made on your site similar to the way you manage comments and other content. This screen is customizable in the same ways as other management screens, and you can act on activities using the on-hover action links or the Bulk Actions.'=>'您可以在您的站台以類似的管理迴響的方式來管理活動等內容。這版面是可以自定和其他管理版面同模樣，您也可停留於活動連結上來進行操作或多項操作。','activity admin edit screenAuthor ID'=>'作者識別碼','activity admin edit screenType'=>'類型','activity admin edit screenLink'=>'連結','activity admin edit screenStatus'=>'狀態','activity admin edit screenPrimary Item/Secondary Item'=>'主要項目/次要項目','<a href="https://buddypress.org/support/">Support Forums</a>'=>'<a href="https://buddypress.org/support/">支援討論</a>','<a href="https://codex.buddypress.org/administrator-guide/activity-stream-management-panels/">Managing Activity</a>'=>'<a href="https://codex.buddypress.org/administrator-guide/activity-stream-management-panels/">管理活動</a>','<strong>Type</strong> - Each distinct kind of activity has its own type. For example, <code>created_group</code> is used when a group is created and <code>joined_group</code> is used when a user joins a group.'=>'<strong>類型</strong> - 每種不同的活動都有自己的類型。 例如： <code>created_group</code> 是使用在群組建立時； <code>joined_group</code> 是使用在使用者加入時。','For information about when and how BuddyPress uses all of these settings, see the Managing Activity link in the panel to the side.'=>'有關 BuddyPress 即將使用的所有設定，請參閱在站台控制台的管理啟動連結。','<strong>Primary Item/Secondary Item</strong> - These identify the object that created the activity. For example, the fields could reference a comment left on a specific site. Some types of activity may only use one, or none, of these fields.'=>'<strong>主要項目／次要項目</strong> - 這些用來識別建立活動的對象。 例如，有些欄位能引用在一個特定站點的迴響。 那些活動類型可能不只引用一個或沒有引用欄位。','Item, Link, Type'=>'項目、連結、類型','The two big editing areas for the activity title and content are fixed in place, but you can reposition all the 